&lt;article class="entry-wrapper no-border" calculateheight="true"&gt;
    &lt;h2 class="articletitle"&gt;World Cup final - Nico the parrot's prediction&lt;/h2&gt;
        &lt;div class="info-container"&gt;
            
                &lt;span class="author"&gt;
                    &lt;span id="ctl00_ArticleDetails_TMI_lblAuthor"&gt;Malta Independent&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;/span&gt;
            
         
            &lt;span class="date-published"&gt;Sunday, 13 July 2014, 12:00&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class="last-update"&gt;Last update: about 11 months ago&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;

        
       
        
        

    &lt;div class="text-container"&gt;
        
        
            &lt;span class="rectangle-ad-container article-ad"&gt;
                 &lt;iframe class='tmiads' id='ad1ea670' name='ad1ea670' data-src='http://ads.independent.com.mt/www/delivery/afr.php?resize=1&amp;zoneid=22&amp;target=_blank&amp;cb=250' frameborder='0' scrolling='no' width='300' height='250' allowtransparency='true'&gt;&lt;a href='http://ads.independent.com.mt/www/delivery/ck.php?n=afef72b0&amp;cb=250' target='_blank'&gt;&lt;img data-src='http://ads.independent.com.mt/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=22&amp;cb=250&amp;n=afef72b0' border='0' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
  
            &lt;/span&gt;
        
       
        &lt;p&gt;
	It&rsquo;s the big day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	The final of the World Cup will be played today in Brazil, pitting Argentina against Germany for the third time in the history of the competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	In 1986, it was Argentina who won, beating Germany 3-2. Four years later, Germany took their revenge with a 1-0 win.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	With their third encounter in the final, this combination is the most common final in 20 World Cup editions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	So, who will win tonight?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Nico the Parrot, of Pet Market, has picked its choice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	The African Gray has managed to guess correctly 17 times, against the 11 times it missed.&lt;/p&gt;
